snippet.title: Super Indie Karts x CrossCode - 150cc Track Play
snippet.description:
Here Comes A New RaceTrack!! - It's Rhombus Square Oval from CrossCode!

Super Indie Karts is a '90s style kart racer available in Early Access on Steam (for Windows and OSX) and OUYA featuring crossovers with a heap of super Indie Games. http://store.steampowered.com/app/323670/

CrossCode is an awesome Action RPG with amazing artwork complete with the smoothest gameplay experience you can find, it was successfully funded on IndieGoGo and is now available on Steam Early Access here: 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/368340/
